cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper is primarily focused on training deep neural networks (DNNs), which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the application of the proposed method on image classification tasks (MNIST, Fashion-MNIST, and CIFAR-10), which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper introduces a new family of methods for training DNNs, which involves permuting neuron connections, which could also be relevant to the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
